description: Normalized log2ratio protein abundance estimates for the Hepatitis B Virus (HBV) Related Hepatocellular Carcinoma Proteome study (PDC000198) were obtained via the PDC API quantDataMatrix endpoint. More information on the pipeline and the results generated by it can be found here: https://pdc.cancer.gov/data-dictionary/harmonization.html
friendlyName: HEPATITIS B VIRUS (HBV) RELATED HEPATOCELLULAR CARCINOMA PROTEOME
